ygData.messageBody:
Here is a question for the masses. I am looking
at 2 video cards. Voodoo 5 5500 and the Prophet II
which one is better. I currently have a ATI rager Fury
but I am wanting to upgrade. I am hoping someone out
there can help me. I am wanting one that has the most
memory but the most reliable. I also hear that Prophet
II Ultra is coming out. anyone heard anything on
this?<br> You can e-mail me if you wish, or post here.<br>
Thanks Mark
